      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THREE HUNDRED (1) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing fourth (23.29) at this track latest. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Has winning claims on her best figures. LET'S TROT WILL (2) started big odds over 400m at The Gardens (23.26) in Grade 5 but ran very well to fill a minor placing. Was a winner the start prior in easier at The Gardens. Has a strong record here at this journey including two wins. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Expected to be in the finish again. STAR PEDRO (7) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from five tries. Below best last time at this track (23.39) in a Grade 5, finishing a 6 length sixth. Looks suited here and can measure up. BROADWAY BABY (8) warrants respect with the drop in trip.",
